OL,3,C'I was left hospitalised after
OL,4,Cswimming in Welsh waters'
OL,6,FA man has said he was scared to drink
OL,7,Ftap water and shower at his home after
OL,8,Fhe became seriously ill after swimming
OL,9,Fin the River Towy.
OL,11,FRobbie Bowman, from Cardiff, was in
OL,12,Fhospital for a week and believes it
OL,13,Fwas down to a cut on his leg that
OL,14,Fbecame infected after swimming near
OL,15,FLlansteffan, Carmarthenshire, in 2022
OL,17,FHe developed cellulitis, an infection
OL,18,Fin the deeper layers of the skin, and
OL,19,Fmore than two years on Robbie's leg
OL,20,Fhas still not fully recovered.
