OL,6,F"I had a very small scratch and didn't
OL,7,Fthink anything about it because we
OL,8,Fwere going to be swimming in the sea,"
OL,9,Fhe told ITV Cymru Wales. "I went in
OL,10,Fand around an hour and a half later
OL,11,Fstarted to feel ill - and this was not
OL,12,Flong after Covid so I thought 'have I
OL,13,Fgot Covid again?'
OL,15,F"I managed to make it home and really
OL,16,Fwas barely able to make it through the
OL,17,Fdoor."
