OL,6,FRobbie was then assessed by a family
OL,7,Ffriend who works as a nurse, and she
OL,8,Fadvised his symptoms indicated an
OL,9,Finfection.
OL,11,F"They (doctors) put me on intravenous
OL,12,Fantibiotics because they were worried
OL,13,Ffrom the blood test they had done that
OL,14,Fthe infection was touching my kidney
OL,15,Fand so the worry was that it would go
OL,16,Fseptic.
OL,18,F"I was in the hospital for a week and
OL,19,Fhad massive blisters on my leg,
OL,20,Fprobably from the antibiotics.
