OL,6,F"From a little scratch, you think the
OL,7,Fsea is going to help it and not going
OL,8,Fto do that. So it was quite full on.'"
OL,10,FRobbie - who said he was a keen open-
OL,11,Fwater swimmer before the incident -
OL,12,Fsays he now does not trust the water
OL,13,Fquality in Welsh rivers and seas
OL,14,Ffollowing the incident.
OL,16,F"It's really put me off swimming
OL,17,Fbecause I love swimming out in the
OL,18,Fwild but I just won't do it now
OL,19,Fbecause I just don't trust anywhere,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
