OL,6,FHowever, exclusive statistics obtained
OL,7,Fby ITV Wales through a Freedom of
OL,8,FInformation request showed that
OL,9,Fbetween the years of 2020-2025, 513
OL,10,Finstances of illnesses were reported
OL,11,Fto Public Health Wales after an
OL,12,Findividual was exposed to water.
OL,14,FThese illnesses range from Giardiasis
OL,15,F(an intestinal infection caused by the
OL,16,FGiardia parasite) to Ecoli.
