OL,6,FRobbie says he was told that his
OL,7,Fcellulitis was likely caused by
OL,8,Fpollution in the sea from suspected
OL,9,Fagriculture run-off infecting his open
OL,10,Fgraze.
OL,12,F"It's hard to prove it because you can
OL,13,Fget cellulitis even from the bacteria
OL,14,Fon your skin but you just think the
OL,15,Fsea is good for cuts and grazes and
OL,16,Fthose sort of things and helps heal
OL,17,Fit," he said.
OL,19,F"But how can you go from an hour and a
OL,20,Fhalf in the sea into infection so
OL,21,Fquickly?"
