OL,6,FRobbie now says he feels there "needs
OL,7,Fto be more done" to protect the
OL,8,Fquality of Welsh waters.
OL,10,F"Fundamentally Natural Resources Wales
OL,11,Fis a good thing but I don't know if
OL,12,Fthey are getting enough support from
OL,13,Fthe government," he said.
OL,15,F"There's lots of uses we have for the
OL,16,Friver and the sea but if they're
OL,17,Fpolluted then that's taking one thing
OL,18,Faway that we can't use, again a
OL,19,Fnatural resource which should be for
OL,20,Fall the people to be able to use and
OL,21,Fto use it safely."
